{
  "id": "adv_love_2603_02_01",
  "title": "Episode 2 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "わざとミスなんてダメだ",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 71.0999871609
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh002.wav",
              "text": "わざとミスするなんてダメに決まってるだろ\n俺は莉央さんに嫌われたくないんだ",
              "startTime": 71.0999871609,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "鈴木",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-suzuki005.wav",
              "text": "女心が分かってないなあ\n女ってのはダメな男に惹かれるものなんだよ",
              "startTime": 76.8333204942,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 7933.345791000008
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio002.wav",
              "text": "惹かれる訳ないでしょ\n私の前でわざとミスなんてしてみなさい\n絶対に許さないから",
              "startTime": 84.6333286323,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "鈴木",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-suzuki006.wav",
              "text": "ひっ……！\nす、すみませんでしたー！",
              "startTime": 92.6666584052,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rui003.wav",
              "text": "どうやら、莉央さんのことは\n{user}君の方が\nよく分かっているみたいね",
              "startTime": 96.6999968247,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "よし、わざとミスしよう",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 101.6666634914
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh003.wav",
              "text": "なるほど、鈴木の言い分にも一理ある\nよし、これからはわざと仕事でミスするぞ！",
              "startTime": 101.6666634914,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 8266.670986199997
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio003.wav",
              "text": "何バカなこと言ってるのよ\n私の前でわざとミスなんてしてみなさい\n初めての恐怖を味わわせてあげるわ",
              "startTime": 109.7999968247,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh004.wav",
              "text": "ひっ……す、すみません……\nおい鈴木\nお前の言ってることはでたらめじゃないか",
              "startTime": 118.6999912299,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "鈴木",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-suzuki007.wav",
              "text": "いやいや、莉央先輩が特殊なんだよ\n世間一般の女子は\nダメ男を可愛いと思うんだって",
              "startTime": 125.7333245632,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh005.wav",
              "text": "世間一般の女子ねぇ……\n瑠依は、ダメ男を可愛いと思うか？",
              "startTime": 134.3333204942,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rui004.wav",
              "text": "私はわざとミスするダメ男より\nいつも真面目な\n{user}君の方が好きよ",
              "startTime": 141.3333204942,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh006.wav",
              "text": "……うん\nやっぱり俺、これからも真面目に働くよ",
              "startTime": 148.1333265977,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "やります！",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 195.2333164252
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh008.wav",
              "text": "やります！\n俺に莉央さんのお手伝いをさせて下さい！",
              "startTime": 195.2333164252,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 8566.689678300008
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio009.wav",
              "text": "いい返事ね\n早速ミーティングを始めるわよ\n私について来なさい",
              "startTime": 199.0666497585,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh009.wav",
              "text": "はい！\nそれじゃあ、瑠依、鈴木\n俺は莉央さんと仕事に戻るからまた後でな",
              "startTime": 205.5666375515,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 5275.556091799985
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rui005.wav",
              "text": "あんなに嬉しそうにして……\n厳しい莉央さんと真面目な彼は\n意外と相性がいいのかもしれないわね",
              "startTime": 212.3333225287,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "自信ないなぁ……",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 220.3999891953
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh010.wav",
              "text": "俺、自信ないです……\n叱られてばかりの俺より\nもっと仕事の出来る人に頼んだ方が……",
              "startTime": 220.3999891953,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rui006.wav",
              "text": "何弱気になってるのよ\nもっと自分に自信を持ちなさい\n大丈夫、あなたなら絶対に出来るわ",
              "startTime": 227.9333235459,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 235.9333296494
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh011.wav",
              "text": "……ありがとう\n瑠依にそう言ってもらえると\nやれそうな気がしてきたよ",
              "startTime": 235.9333296494,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 240.7333296494
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh012.wav",
              "text": "莉央さん。やっぱり俺、プロジェクトに\n参加します。莉央さんの期待に\n応えられるように頑張ります",
              "startTime": 240.7333296494,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio010.wav",
              "text": "いい返事ね\nじゃあ、ミーティングをするから\n後で私の所に来なさい",
              "startTime": 247.6666629828,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 7210.015890899996
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh013.wav",
              "text": "分かりました！\nよーし、莉央さんをサポート出来るように\nなってやるぞ！",
              "startTime": 254.0999963161,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rui007.wav",
              "text": "その意気よ\n応援してるから、頑張ってね",
              "startTime": 259.4999963161,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "嘘をついて定時退社する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 305.0333377875
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh016.wav",
              "text": "あの……\n莉央さん、ちょっといいですか？",
              "startTime": 305.0333377875,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio011.wav",
              "text": "どうしたの？　頼んでいた資料作りは\nもう終わったのかしら？\n終わっていないのなら仕事に戻って……",
              "startTime": 309.8000044541,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh017.wav",
              "text": "いえ……\nちょっと体調が悪いので\n今日はもう帰っていいですか？",
              "startTime": 317.1666690863,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio012.wav",
              "text": "はあ？　体調が悪いですって？\n貴方――",
              "startTime": 322.6666690863,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh018.wav",
              "text": "や、やっぱりダメですよね！？\nすみません、ちょっと言ってみただけで……\nすぐに仕事に戻りま――",
              "startTime": 327.799992247,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio013.wav",
              "text": "ばか！　どうして早く言わないのよ！\n体調が悪いのなら無理しないで\nすぐに帰って休みなさい！",
              "startTime": 333.5999942816,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh019.wav",
              "text": "え、でも仕事が……",
              "startTime": 341.1666568793,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-rio014.wav",
              "text": "そんなことより自分の体を第一に考えなさい\nほら、早く帰りなさい",
              "startTime": 343.4999637641,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_02_01-koh020.wav",
              "text": "は、はい……\nじゃあ、お先に失礼します……",
              "startTime": 349.4666385688,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "――翌日",
              "startTime": 355.3333455403,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 1366.6565258000105
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
